    a: "Jay Trainer has performed at venues across the Pittsburgh area, San Francisco, and beyond. Live recordings from the San Francisco era appear on A Whisper Of Ruin — Deluxe Edition, including Voodoo Chile (Live) and Of The Sun (Live). For upcoming show dates and booking inquiries, check the website and social media channels."
  - q: "How does Jay Trainer record music?"
